# WS-Discovery (OASIS, udp:3702) Probe message. A SOAP 1.2 envelope (XML) multicast to
# 239.255.255.250:3702 with a WS-Addressing Action of .../discovery/Probe. The whole datagram payload is
# kept verbatim (byte-perfect); the Action URI is parsed for display. tshark dissects the payload as xml
# (eth:ethertype:ip:udp:xml). source: synthetic WS-Discovery Probe frame built to spec; IPv4/UDP headers
# and UDP checksum computed by hand, dst MAC 01:00:5e:7f:ff:fa (IPv4 multicast for 239.255.255.250).

